{
  "stem": "14708.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of her human feeling, human feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was in, in prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a few days, Jan-- yeah, no, there was one episode I must say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was taken to the prison, ev-everybody was stripped and checked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a blouse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here was a little pocket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had with me a picture of my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I folded it and put it in that pocket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when it was my turn to strip, then I took off the blouse already so the woman who did the searching, she didn't notice that I have a picture in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this picture was with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After a few days, I was, in evening, I was standing in the door of our cell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one of the-- what is it called-- one of the policemen, one of the--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guard, yeah, one of the guard came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he started to touch me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he opened my blouse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he touched my breast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he said, what do you have here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, that's my mother's picture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He took away his hand and said, ah, go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew at that moment that my mother, who didn't live at that time anymore, but she saved me from that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After a few days, I asked a policeman-- on this picture on the other side, I wrote a few words to my father that I am [INAUDIBLE] here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if he can, he should help me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I must also tell that I didn't tell this that after I left from the ghetto, just a fe-- two or three days after that, my father and also my cousin were taken to labor camps.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my mother and grandmother stayed there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
